src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嗰位巴打應該係指吞拿魚嗰類副食罐<br />\n嗰啲大貓都唔應該餵太多<br />\n貓仔更加唔好，上左癮真係好難戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 尤其貓咁有性格<br />\n呢類通常啲人用嚟吸引病貓食，貪佢夠重味夠香</blockquote><br />\n你講我隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}